00:03:09.820 --> 00:03:10.540
Como dije,

00:03:11.380 --> 00:03:12.060
si terminas lo que quieres hacer,

00:03:12.860 --> 00:03:13.740
vete rápido.

00:03:15.260 --> 00:03:15.690
Vete.

00:03:34.850 --> 00:03:35.650
Tía.

00:03:36.260 --> 00:03:38.280
